========================================================================
===================       SCRIB IRC CHATBOT        =====================
========================================================================

License:        GNU AGPLv3 or later
Author:         Sina Mashek & The Whube Developers
Email:          tenach [ at ] whube [ dot ] com

========================================================================
===================        WHAT YOU NEED           =====================
========================================================================

* python-irclib
	 ( http://python-irclib.sourceforge.net/ 
	   Most distros: install python-irclib			       )

========================================================================
===================        INITIAL SETUP           =====================
========================================================================

* Please set conf/scrib-irc.cfg to taste before running.

========================================================================
===================        OPTIONAL DERP           =====================
========================================================================

* espeak
	(  http://espeak.sourceforge.net/
	   If you wish to use the voice-grue or voice-scrib, you'll
	   need to install espeak.
	   Most distros: install espeak				       )

========================================================================
===================            NOTES               =====================
========================================================================

* feedme.py lets you fill scrib's brain with text from a file.
* Will be moving to using PyBrain. Maybe. Eventually.


